<p>A systems-thinking coach. Helps you draw and refine systems diagrams — naming components, drawing arrows in the correct causal direction, and labeling feedback loops as positive (amplifying) or negative (stabilizing). Launches in <strong>Unit 1 Block 2</strong> as your first systems-thinking class; high value again in Block 7 (Habitability Framework) and across <strong>Units 2, 4, 5, and 6</strong> whenever you're working with a complex Earth or human system.</p>

